snippet.textDisplay:
This keeps happening every day, he truly is like a forest fire while everyone else in the world is just your average campfire. Every time he's on stage the props look luxurious, the set cinematographic, his expressions those of a movie star, his moves elegant and refined, I have no words to describe his impact properly because it's unprecedented. To put it mildly, he's a legend in the making, but honestly, there's no art form he won't conquer! I expect great things from him and he always ends up exceeding my expectations. I miss the days when I didn't know anything about him and could fully experience all that Seokjin power for the first time. But I don't have to worry too much, because I know he will find new ways to impress everyone and his debut as an actor will change the industry forever. He has changed the way I view music, artists, singers, men and his debut will not be the exception.
